      ch\u01A1i ti\u1EBFp theo."
    english: Deploy the selected scenario on the next run.
  - key: levelselect.level.training_map.name
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0110\u1ED3 Hu\u1EA5n Luy\u1EC7n"
    english: Training Map
  - key: levelselect.level.training_map.description
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n c\xF3 h\u01B0\u1EDBng
      d\u1EABn, d\xF9ng \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m quen v\u1EDBi \u0111i\u1EC1u khi\u1EC3n
      v\xE0 lu\u1ED3ng ch\u01A1i."
    english: A guided training map used for onboarding and control familiarization.
  - key: levelselect.level.training_map.objective
    vietnamese: "Tri\u1EC3n khai v\xE0o b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n
      v\xE0 ho\xE0n th\xE0nh k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n h\u01B0\u1EDBng d\u1EABn."
    english: Deploy into the training map and complete the tutorial scenario.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_map_01.name
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0110\u1ED3 1"
    english: Map 1
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_map_01.description
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 khu d\xE2n c\u01B0 c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u t\xECnh
      hu\u1ED1ng s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1 c\xF3 th\u1EC3 x\u1EA3y ra. Ch\u1EC9 khi tri\u1EC3n
      khai m\u1EDBi bi\u1EBFt ch\xEDnh x\xE1c k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n."
    english: A suburban residential map with multiple possible incidents. The exact
      scenario will only be revealed after deployment.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_map_01.objective
    vietnamese: "Tri\u1EC3n khai \u0111\u1EBFn b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 v\xE0 x\u1EED
      l\xFD k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c g\xE1n ng\u1EABu nhi\xEAn."
    english: Deploy to the map and respond to the randomly assigned scenario.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_map_02.name
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0110\u1ED3 2"
    english: Map 2
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_map_02.description
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 d\xE2n c\u01B0 hi\u1EC7n \u0111ang tri\u1EC3n
      khai k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n ch\xE1y garage."
    english: A residential map that currently deploys a garage fire scenario.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_map_02.objective
    vietnamese: "Tri\u1EC3n khai \u0111\u1EBFn b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 v\xE0 x\u1EED
      l\xFD k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c g\xE1n ng\u1EABu nhi\xEAn."
    english: Deploy to the map and respond to the randomly assigned scenario.
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_01.name
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0110\u1ED3 3"
    english: Map 3
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_01.description
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 n\xE0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1EC3
      tr\u1ED1ng cho c\u1EA5u h\xECnh k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n sau n\xE0y."
    english: This city map is reserved for future scenario setup.
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_01.objective
    vietnamese: "G\xE1n k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF kho\xE1 b\u1EA3n
      \u0111\u1ED3 n\xE0y."
    english: Assign scenarios to enable this map.
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_02.name
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0110\u1ED3 4"
    english: Map 4
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_02.description
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 n\xE0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1EC3
      tr\u1ED1ng cho c\u1EA5u h\xECnh k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n sau n\xE0y."
    english: This city map is reserved for future scenario setup.
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_02.objective
    vietnamese: "G\xE1n k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF kho\xE1 b\u1EA3n
