  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_03.description
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ED3 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 n\xE0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1EC3
      tr\u1ED1ng cho c\u1EA5u h\xECnh k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n sau n\xE0y."
    english: This city map is reserved for future scenario setup.
  - key: levelselect.level.city_map_03.objective
    vietnamese: "G\xE1n k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF kho\xE1 b\u1EA3n
