  - key: levelselect.scenario.training_map_tutorial.name
    vietnamese: "H\u01B0\u1EDBng D\u1EABn"
    english: Tutorial
  - key: levelselect.scenario.suburban_map_01_kitchen_fire.name
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y B\u1EBFp"
    english: Kitchen Fire
  - key: levelselect.scenario.suburban_map_01_kitchen_fire.description
    vietnamese: "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi g\u1ECDi b\xE1o c\xF3 ch\xE1y b\u1EBFp trong m\u1ED9t
      c\u0103n nh\xE0 khu d\xE2n c\u01B0. H\xE3y thu th\u1EADp th\xF4ng tin \u0111i\u1EC1u
      ph\u1ED1i v\xE0 \u1ED5n \u0111\u1ECBnh cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi."
    english: Caller reports a kitchen fire in a suburban house. Collect the dispatch
      details and stabilize the call.
  - key: levelselect.scenario.suburban_map_01_laundry_room_fire.name
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y Ph\xF2ng Gi\u1EB7t"
    english: Laundry Room Fire
  - key: levelselect.scenario.suburban_map_01_laundry_room_fire.description
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y ph\xF2ng gi\u1EB7t c\xF3 c\u1EA3 nguy c\u01A1 gas l\u1EABn
      \u0111i\u1EC7n. H\xE3y thu th\u1EADp \u0111\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EE7 b\xE1o c\xE1o
      v\xE0 \u0111\xE1nh gi\xE1 m\u1EE9c \u0111\u1ED9 nghi\xEAm tr\u1ECDng."
    english: Laundry room fire with both gas and electrical hazards present. Collect
      the full report and assess the incident severity.
  - key: levelselect.scenario.suburban_map_02_garage_fire.name
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y Garage"
    english: Garage Fire
  - key: levelselect.scenario.suburban_map_02_garage_fire.description
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y garage khi v\u1EABn c\xF2n ng\u01B0\u1EDDi gi\xE0 b\xEAn
      trong, l\u1EA1i c\xF3 nhi\xEAn li\u1EC7u v\xE0 v\u1EADt d\u1EE5ng d\u1EC5 ch\xE1y
      \u1EDF g\u1EA7n."
    english: Garage fire with an elderly parent still inside, fuel containers nearby,
      and a fast-moving interior risk.
  - key: levelselect.level.tutorial.name
    vietnamese: "H\u01B0\u1EDBng D\u1EABn"
    english: Tutorial
  - key: levelselect.level.tutorial.description
