  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.name
    vietnamese: "Cu\u1ED9c G\u1ECDi Ch\xE1y B\u1EBFp"
    english: Kitchen Fire House Call
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.category
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y Nh\xE0"
    english: House Fire
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.description
    vietnamese: "K\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n ch\xE1y b\u1EBFp g\u1ED3m thu th\u1EADp th\xF4ng
      tin, x\xE1c nh\u1EADn l\u1EA1i, \u0111\xE1nh gi\xE1 r\u1EE7i ro, n\u1ED9p b\xE1o
      c\xE1o v\xE0 xem k\u1EBFt qu\u1EA3."
    english: Kitchen-fire call prototype with follow-up collection, confirmation
      read-back, assess-risk, submit, and result review.
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_laundry_fire.name
    vietnamese: "Nh\xE0 D\xE2n C\u01B0 - Ch\xE1y Ph\xF2ng Gi\u1EB7t"
    english: Suburban House - Laundry Room Fire
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_laundry_fire.category
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y Nh\xE0"
    english: House Fire
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_laundry_fire.description
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y ph\xF2ng gi\u1EB7t c\xF3 c\u1EA3 nguy c\u01A1 gas l\u1EABn
      \u0111i\u1EC7n, kh\xF3i lan v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa b\u1EBFp, v\xE0 v\u1EABn c\xF2n
      m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\u1EDBn b\xEAn trong."
    english: Laundry room fire with both gas and electrical hazards present, smoke
      spreading toward the kitchen, and one adult still inside.
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_garage_fire.name
    vietnamese: "Nh\xE0 D\xE2n C\u01B0 - Ch\xE1y Garage"
    english: Suburban House - Garage Fire
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_garage_fire.category
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y Nh\xE0"
    english: House Fire
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_garage_fire.description
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y garage khi v\u1EABn c\xF2n ng\u01B0\u1EDDi gi\xE0 b\xEAn
      trong, g\u1EA7n c\xF3 th\xF9ng nhi\xEAn li\u1EC7u, v\xE0 ng\u1ECDn l\u1EEDa
      \u0111ang lan v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa h\xE0nh lang."
    english: Garage fire with an elderly parent still inside, fuel containers nearby,
      and fire spreading toward the hallway.
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.ask_address
    vietnamese: "\u0110\u1ECBa ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 g\xEC?"
    english: What is the address?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.intro_operator_open
    vietnamese: "911, b\u1EA1n c\u1EA7n tr\u1EE3 gi\xFAp g\xEC?"
    english: 911, where is your emergency?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.intro_caller_open
    vietnamese: "Nh\xE0 t\xF4i \u0111ang ch\xE1y! Xin h\xE3y gi\xFAp v\u1EDBi!"
    english: My house is on fire! Please help!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.intro_operator_fire_location
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xE1m ch\xE1y \u0111ang \u1EDF \u0111\xE2u ngay l\xFAc n\xE0y?"
    english: Where is the fire right now?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.intro_caller_fire_location
    vietnamese: "N\xF3 \u1EDF trong b\u1EBFp, kh\xF3i \u0111ang m\u1ECBt kh\u1EAFp
      n\u01A1i!"
    english: It's in the kitchen, there's smoke everywhere!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.intro_caller_fire_location_0
    vietnamese: "b\u1EBFp"
    english: kitchen
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.intro_caller_fire_location_1
    vietnamese: "kh\xF3i m\u1ECBt kh\u1EAFp n\u01A1i"
    english: smoke everywhere
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.reply_address
    vietnamese: "L\xE0 27 Maple Street!"
    english: It's 27 Maple Street!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.reply_address_0
    vietnamese: 27 Maple Street
    english: 27 Maple Street
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.ask_occupant_risk
    vietnamese: "C\xF2n ai b\xEAn trong kh\xF4ng?"
    english: Is anyone still inside?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.reply_occupant_risk
    vietnamese: "Con t\xF4i v\u1EABn \u1EDF tr\xEAn l\u1EA7u!"
    english: My child is upstairs!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.reply_occupant_risk_0
    vietnamese: "con t\xF4i v\u1EABn \u1EDF tr\xEAn l\u1EA7u"
    english: child is upstairs
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.ask_hazard
    vietnamese: "C\xF3 r\xF2 r\u1EC9 gas ho\u1EB7c b\xECnh gas \u1EDF g\u1EA7n \u0111\xF3
      kh\xF4ng?"
    english: Is there any gas leak or gas cylinder nearby?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.reply_hazard
    vietnamese: "C\xF3, c\xF3 m\u1ED9t b\xECnh gas g\u1EA7n b\u1EBFp!"
    english: Yes, there's a gas cylinder near the kitchen!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.reply_hazard_0
    vietnamese: "b\xECnh gas g\u1EA7n b\u1EBFp"
    english: gas cylinder near the kitchen
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.ask_spread_status
    vietnamese: "L\u1EEDa c\xF3 \u0111ang lan sang \u0111\xE2u kh\xE1c kh\xF4ng?"
    english: Is the fire spreading anywhere else?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.reply_spread_status
    vietnamese: "L\u1EEDa \u0111ang lan v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa khu b\xE0n \u0103n!"
    english: It's spreading toward the dining area!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.reply_spread_status_0
    vietnamese: "lan v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa khu b\xE0n \u0103n"
    english: spreading toward the dining area
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.ask_caller_safety
    vietnamese: "Hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i b\u1EA1n c\xF3 \u0111ang \u1EDF n\u01A1i an to\xE0n
      kh\xF4ng?"
    english: Are you somewhere safe right now?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.reply_caller_safety
    vietnamese: "V\xE2ng, gi\u1EDD t\xF4i \u0111ang \u1EDF ngo\xE0i nh\xE0!"
    english: Yes, I'm outside the house now!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.reply_caller_safety_0
    vietnamese: "ngo\xE0i nh\xE0"
    english: outside the house
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.confirm_address_operator
    vietnamese: "Cho t\xF4i x\xE1c nh\u1EADn l\u1EA1i \u0111\u1ECBa ch\u1EC9: 27
      Maple Street, \u0111\xFAng kh\xF4ng?"
    english: 'Let me confirm the address: 27 Maple Street, correct?'
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.confirm_address_caller
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xFAng r\u1ED3i."
    english: Yes, that's correct.
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.confirm_address_caller_0
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xFAng r\u1ED3i."
    english: Yes, that's correct.
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.confirm_occupant_operator
    vietnamese: "Con c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n v\u1EABn c\xF2n \u1EDF tr\xEAn l\u1EA7u, \u0111\xFAng
      kh\xF4ng?"
    english: Your child is still upstairs, correct?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.confirm_occupant_caller
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xFAng!"
    english: Yes!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.confirm_occupant_caller_0
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xFAng!"
    english: Yes!
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.confirm_safety_operator
    vietnamese: "Hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i b\u1EA1n \u0111ang \u1EDF ngo\xE0i nh\xE0, \u0111\xFAng
      kh\xF4ng?"
    english: You are outside the house now, correct?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.line.confirm_safety_caller
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xFAng, t\xF4i \u0111ang \u1EDF ngo\xE0i."
    english: Yes, I'm outside.
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.span.confirm_safety_caller_0
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xFAng, t\xF4i \u0111ang \u1EDF ngo\xE0i."
    english: Yes, I'm outside.
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.question.kitchen_q_address_exact
    vietnamese: "\u0110\u1ECBa ch\u1EC9 ch\xEDnh x\xE1c l\xE0 g\xEC?"
    english: What is the exact address?
