      kh\xF4ng?"
    english: Are you somewhere safe right now?
  - key: callphase.scenario.kitchen_fire_house_call.question.kitchen_q_pet_inside
    vietnamese: "C\xF3 th\xFA c\u01B0ng n\xE0o v\u1EABn c\xF2n trong nh\xE0 kh\xF4ng?"
