  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_garage_fire.question_reply.garage_q_insurance
    vietnamese: "T\xF4i kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1EBFn b\u1EA3o hi\u1EC3m
      l\xFAc n\xE0y, t\xF4i ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA7n gi\xFAp \u0111\u1EE1!"
    english: I can't think about insurance right now, I just need help here!
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_garage_fire.question.garage_q_when_started
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xE1m ch\xE1y b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u v\xE0o kho\u1EA3ng th\u1EDDi
      gian n\xE0o?"
    english: About what time did the fire start?
  - key: callphase.scenario.suburban_house_garage_fire.question_reply.garage_q_when_started
    vietnamese: "N\xF3 m\u1EDBi x\u1EA3y ra th\xF4i, xin h\xE3y g\u1EEDi l\u1EF1c
      l\u01B0\u1EE3ng ch\u1EEFa ch\xE1y \u0111\u1EBFn nhanh!"
    english: It happened just now, please send the fire department fast!
