    english: Severity was lower than expected.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.strong_followup
    vietnamese: "B\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 \u01B0u ti\xEAn c\xE1c c\xE2u h\u1ECFi b\u1ED5 sung kh\xE1 h\u1EE3p l\xFD."
    english: You generally prioritized relevant follow-up questions.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.mixed_followup
    vietnamese: "M\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 c\xE2u h\u1ECFi b\u1ED5 sung h\u1EEFu \xEDch, nh\u01B0ng m\u1EE9c \u0111\u1ED9 \u01B0u ti\xEAn ch\u01B0a \u0111\u1EC1u."
    english: Some follow-up questions were useful, but prioritization was uneven.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.poor_followup
    vietnamese: "M\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 c\xE2u h\u1ECFi b\u1ED5 sung c\xF3 \u0111\u1ED9 \u01B0u ti\xEAn th\u1EA5p h\u01A1n so v\u1EDBi t\xECnh hu\u1ED1ng."
    english: Some follow-up questions were lower priority than the situation required.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.all_confirmed
    vietnamese: "C\xE1c th\xF4ng tin quan tr\u1ECDng \u0111\u00E3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c x\xE1c nh\u1EADn."
    english: Critical facts were confirmed.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.none_confirmed
    vietnamese: "Ch\u01B0a c\xF3 th\xF4ng tin quan tr\u1ECDng n\xE0o \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c x\xE1c nh\u1EADn."
    english: No critical facts were confirmed.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.partial_confirmed
    vietnamese: "C\u1EA7n x\xE1c nh\u1EADn l\u1EA1i nhi\u1EC1u th\xF4ng tin quan tr\u1ECDng h\u01A1n."
    english: More read-back confirmation was needed for critical facts.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.strong_correctness
    vietnamese: "C\xE1c chi ti\u1EBFt s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1 quan tr\u1ECDng kh\u1EDBp t\u1ED1t v\u1EDBi k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n."
    english: Key incident details matched the scenario well.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.ready_to_submit
    vietnamese: "B\xE1o c\xE1o \u0111\u00E3 s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng \u0111\u1EC3 n\u1ED9p."
    english: Report was ready to submit.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.incomplete_submission
    vietnamese: "V\u1EABn c\xF2n m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 chi ti\u1EBFt thi\u1EBFu khi n\u1ED9p b\xE1o c\xE1o."
    english: Some report details were missing at submission.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.call_time_good
    vietnamese: "T\u1ED1c \u0111\u1ED9 x\u1EED l\xFD cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi hi\u1EC7u qu\u1EA3 cho k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n n\xE0y."
    english: Call handling was efficient for this scenario.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.call_time_acceptable
    vietnamese: "T\u1ED1c \u0111\u1ED9 x\u1EED l\xFD cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi ch\u1EA5p nh\u1EADn \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c, nh\u01B0ng c\xF3 th\u1EC3 nhanh h\u01A1n."
    english: Call handling pace was acceptable, but could be faster.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.call_time_slow
    vietnamese: "Th\u1EDDi gian x\u1EED l\xFD cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi l\xE2u h\u01A1n m\u1EE5c ti\xEAu c\u1EE7a k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n."
    english: Call handling took longer than the scenario target.
  - key: callphase.result.feedback.call_time_not_scored
    vietnamese: "Hi\u1EC7u qu\u1EA3 th\u1EDDi gian cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi kh\xF4ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\xEDnh v\xEC b\xE1o c\xE1o n\u1ED9p ch\u01B0a \u0111\u1EE7 ho\xE0n ch\u1EC9nh."
