  - key: mission.tutorial.description
    vietnamese: "M\u1EDF c\u1ED5ng, kh\u1ED1ng ch\u1EBF \u0111\xE1m ch\xE1y, r\u1ED3i di chuy\u1EC3n t\u1EDBi \u0111i\u1EC3m tho\xE1t."
    english: Open the gate, contain the fire, then move to the extraction point.
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.open_gate.title
    vietnamese: "M\u1EDF c\u1ED5ng"
    english: Open the Gate
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.open_gate.description
    vietnamese: "D\xF9ng c\u1ED5ng \u0111\u1EC3 v\xE0o khu hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n."
    english: Use the gate to enter the training yard.
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.contain_fire.title
    vietnamese: "Kh\u1ED1ng ch\u1EBF \u0111\xE1m ch\xE1y"
    english: Contain the Fire
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.contain_fire.description
    vietnamese: "Nh\u1EB7t v\xF2i v\xE0 d\u1EADp c\xE1c \u0111\xE1m ch\xE1y trong s\xE2n."
    english: Pick up the hose and extinguish the fires inside the yard.
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.break_barricade.title
    vietnamese: "Ph\xE1 ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i"
    english: Break the Barricade
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.break_barricade.description
    vietnamese: "Ph\xE1 ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF l\u1ED1i \u0111i b\u1ECB ch\u1EB7n."
    english: Clear the blocked path by breaking the barricade.
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.rescue_victim.title
    vietnamese: "C\u1EE9u n\u1EA1n nh\xE2n"
    english: Rescue the Victim
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.rescue_victim.description
    vietnamese: "\u0110\u01B0a n\u1EA1n nh\xE2n t\u1EDBi khu v\u1EF1c an to\xE0n."
    english: Carry the victim to the safe zone.
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.reach_exit.title
    vietnamese: "Ra \u0111i\u1EC3m tho\xE1t"
    english: Reach the Exit
  - key: mission.tutorial.stage.reach_exit.description
    vietnamese: "Di theo l\u1ED1i \u0111\u00E3 m\u1EDF v\xE0 b\u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0o khu v\u1EF1c tho\xE1t."
    english: Move through the cleared route and step into the extraction area.
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.open_gate.title
    vietnamese: "M\u1EDF c\u1ED5ng"
    english: Open the Gate
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.open_gate.description
    vietnamese: "T\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c v\u1EDBi c\u1ED5ng l\u01B0\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EC3 v\xE0o khu s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1."
    english: Interact with the chainlink gate to access the incident area.
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.open_gate.pending
    vietnamese: "T\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c v\u1EDBi c\u1ED5ng \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng"
    english: Interact with the gate to open the route
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.open_gate.completed
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xE3 m\u1EDF c\u1ED5ng"
    english: Gate opened
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.contain_fire.title
    vietnamese: "Kh\u1ED1ng ch\u1EBF \u0111\xE1m ch\xE1y"
    english: Contain the Fire
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.contain_fire.description
    vietnamese: "D\u1EADp t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 \u0111\xE1m ch\xE1y nh\xECn th\u1EA5y trong s\xE2n."
    english: Extinguish all visible fires inside the yard.
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.break_barricade.title
    vietnamese: "Ph\xE1 ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i"
    english: Break the Barricade
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.break_barricade.description
    vietnamese: "Ph\xE1 ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF l\u1ED1i."
    english: Break the barricade to clear the route.
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.break_barricade.pending
    vietnamese: "Ph\xE1 ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i"
    english: Break target
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.break_barricade.completed
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xE3 ph\xE1 ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i"
    english: Target broken
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.rescue_victim.title
    vietnamese: "C\u1EE9u n\u1EA1n nh\xE2n"
    english: Rescue Victim Objective
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.rescue_victim.description
    vietnamese: "\u0110\u01B0a n\u1EA1n nh\xE2n t\u1EDBi v\xF9ng an to\xE0n."
    english: Bring Victim To Safe Zone
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.rescue_victim.pending
    vietnamese: "\u0110\u01B0a n\u1EA1n nh\xE2n t\u1EDBi v\xF9ng an to\xE0n"
    english: Deliver target to safe zone
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.rescue_victim.completed
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xE3 \u0111\u01B0a n\u1EA1n nh\xE2n t\u1EDBi v\xF9ng an to\xE0n"
    english: Target delivered to safe zone
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.reach_exit.title
    vietnamese: "Ra \u0111i\u1EC3m tho\xE1t"
    english: Reach the Exit
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.reach_exit.description
    vietnamese: "Di chuy\u1EC3n v\xE0o khu v\u1EF1c tho\xE1t sau khi \u0111\xE1m ch\xE1y \u0111\u00E3 t\u1EAFt."
    english: Move into the highlighted extraction area after the fire is out.
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.reach_exit.pending
    vietnamese: "Di chuy\u1EC3n t\u1EDBi \u0111i\u1EC3m tho\xE1t"
    english: Move to the extraction point
  - key: mission.tutorial.objective.reach_exit.completed
    vietnamese: "\u0110\xE3 t\u1EDBi \u0111i\u1EC3m tho\xE1t"
    english: Extraction point reached
  - key: mission.tutorial.fail.time_limit.title
    vietnamese: "Gi\u1EDBi h\u1EA1n th\u1EDDi gian"
    english: Tutorial Time Limit
  - key: mission.tutorial.fail.time_limit.description
    vietnamese: "Ho\xE0n th\xE0nh ph\u1EA7n h\u01B0\u1EDBng d\u1EABn tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi h\u1EBFt gi\u1EDD."
    english: Finish the tutorial before time runs out.
